Global Niacinamide for Personal Care Market Insights
Niacinamide for Personal Care Market size was valued at USD 1.8 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.0 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Niacinamide for Personal Care Market Overview
The global Niacinamide for Personal Care market is experiencing substantial growth, with an estimated market size of USD 1.21 billion in 2023 and expected to reach USD 2.3 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.6% during the forecast period. This surge is driven by the increasing consumer demand for skincare products that offer multiple benefits, such as anti-aging, brightening, and anti-inflammatory properties. As a versatile ingredient, niacinamide has been integrated into a wide range of products, including moisturizers, serums, and sunscreens, which has enhanced its market penetration globally.

